After you complete setup, CRM Analytics Direct Data for Google BigQuery lets you run queries on the dataset associated with the connection in real time. You can also build dashboard charts and tables based on the queries you run on Google BigQuery data.

To create live connections to Google BigQuery: Enable CRM Analytics Direct Data for external data sources
To explore data directly in Google BigQuery: Explore External Data Directly

To begin exploring, click the live dataset from the Datasets tab in Analytics Studio.
